reviews.text: Great taste for ramen until my son have 2 bowl to eat in here 😆😆😍
Genuinely one of the best ramen places in Hong Kong. I would recommend it to anyone who likes ramen.
Clean , spacious, pork soup is very thick
Hands down, the best ramen ever.Rich broth with a full flavour. Good prices, fast service.

The Best Ramen I have tried in Hong Kong. I recommend the lobster ramen and the fried dumplings. Affordable and delicious. It is, however, a not-so spacious restaurant. It's a bit small inside and you have a tendency to touch each other's elbow. 😁

reviews.text: 不了，上等豚肉，變咗街市瘦肉。糖心蛋冇味
燒豚肉好食. 枝豆好大碟, 起碼要兩個人先得
食物質素一般而價錢高。服務質素差劣，香港人去到三個人唔畀坐四人枱。但係洋人兩個人就可以坐。埋單時有部信用卡機都唔肯收信用卡，迫人畀現金或八達通。
Great taste for ramen until my son have 2 bowl to eat in here 😆😆😍
